{"tid":2245862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國政局簡述","createTime":"2020-10-16T14:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T05:50:41.000Z","uid":222614,"like":45,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"49856bacbe9a42bb9e1a7c2c965ec1a0baa4b890","tid":2245862,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"當今美國政局變化因素主要係兩個勢力「大美國陣營」同「影子政府」之間嘅內鬥<br />\n<br />\n影子政府掌控民主黨，媒體，金融，學術機構，藥廠等等<br />\n<br />\n而大美國陣營嘅組成主要有政府，軍方，企業等等<br />\n<br />\n最近大家都見，大美國陣營嘗試披露對影子政府不利嘅消息，係受影子政府操縱嘅社交媒體被封閉<br />\n<br />\n顯示大美國陣營正在尋求黎自民間嘅更多支持卻遇到好大阻力"},{"pid":"52d59473be8d680dd95db0a9b79f0642262e5ac9","tid":2245862,"uid":84275,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"點分大美國/影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨就影子政府，共和黨就大美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d72bd760ad8629c3832a0544905b75acfc7989","tid":2245862,"uid":222614,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"52d59473be8d680dd95db0a9b79f0642262e5ac9","tid":2245862,"uid":84275,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"點分大美國/影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨就影子政府，共和黨就大美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:30:53.000Z","msg":"影子政府 = deep state <br />\n<br />\n係 Trump 自己爆出黎"},{"pid":"f9e02a9bbb6b586582adae350fe101385d91dd4e","tid":2245862,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"大美國陣營正在爭扎保住總統個位"},{"pid":"2f038c57f7ffd67b114eaf5f0f45f7baa21a81da","tid":2245862,"uid":222614,"lik